headline: Gonzaga University and U.S. Bank Expand Partnership With a New Debit Card Design
summary: SPOKANE, Wash., May 21, 2025--Gonzaga University supporters can now show their school pride with the new U.S. Bank Visa® Debit Card with the Gonzaga University design from U.S. Bank. The card was launched on May 11, 2025, and features College Hall, the campus’ oldest building.
